snippet.title: TEALERLAND - Trailer 2
snippet.description:
(Originally premiered on the Fangames at Freddy's live-stream event.)
Get a glimpse of what's above the ground in the second trailer for TEALERLAND, and survive the storage facility beneath in the newly released 2.0 demo: https://gamejolt.com/games/TEALERLAND/466109

TEALERLAND is a challenging fan-made Five Nights at Freddy's tribute featuring the return of the 2015 character Tealer along with some new, never before seen friends.

( Music: Sound The Alarm by Really Slow Motion; ending composition custom-made by NotAlexFalkenberg )
